{"tid":1852557,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[和你進出] 如何成為立法會進出口界功能組別選民？","createTime":"2020-01-30T13:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T11:01:06.000Z","uid":47194,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0ea3f3599e451589ac9e5c806dd8c90f422e0336","tid":1852557,"uid":47194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T13:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FbPFLhL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFbPFLhL.jpg&h=9de3fd1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是咁的，要成為功能組别進出口界選民，只需要符合下列條件當中一項即可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n(1) 根據《應課稅品條例》(第 109章)領有進口或 出口或進口及出口應課稅品牌照的公司；<br />\n(2) 在緊接《2008 年應課稅品(修訂)(第 2 號)條例》(2008 年第 16 號)生效之前根據《應課稅品條例》(第 109 章)領有進口(或 進口及出口)飲用酒類牌照的公司；<br />\n(3) 根據《汽車(首次登記稅）條例》(第 330 章)註冊從事進口供在香港使用的汽車的公司；<br />\n(4) 根據《化學品管制條例》(第 145 章)領有輸入或輸出或輸入及輸出受管制化學品牌照的公司；<br />\n<br />\n或(5)有權在以下任何團體的大會上表決的該團體的成員或會員：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港攝影器材進口商會有限公司</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\napeihk@gmail.com<br />\nG.P.O Box 13373, Central Post Office , Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n<strong>港九鋼材五金進出口商會有限公司</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中環德輔道中287-291號長達大廈10樓<br />\n2545 2356<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港中華出入口商會</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港中環德輔道中287-291號長達大廈7-8樓<br />\n2544 8474<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港出口商會</strong><br />\nRm. 924, Star House, 3 Salisbury Road, Tsimshatsui, Kowloon<br />\n2730 9851<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港食用油進出口商總會有限公司</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九龍灣啓祥道20號8樓<br />\n2768 2133<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港進出口米商聯合會</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上環德輔道西81-85號潮州會館301室<br />\n2547 7323<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港鐘錶入口商會</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港中環皇后大道中58-62號振邦大廈604室<br />\n2523 3232<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港食品，飲料及雜貨協會</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nG.P.O. Box 8689, Hong Kong<br />\n2923 8419<br />\n<br />\n<strong>港九輕工業品進出口商商會有限公司</strong><br />\n1/F, Back Stall, Nam Pak Hong Building, 22-28 Bonham Strand West, Sheung Wan<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港南洋輸出入商會</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n德輔道中287～291長達大厦9F/905<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">進出口界現況：黃定光自動當選16年</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目前進出口界選民只有1342名(含團體票842及個人票501)，現任議員黃定光，民建聯成員，於2004年9月在無競爭對手競逐下，循功能界別自動當選為香港立法會議員(進出口界)，並於同年獲授銅紫荊星章。<br />\n<br />\n及後的2008年、2012年及2016年，黃定光都自動當選進出口界立法會議員，即是說該界別選民近二十年來從未投過票，有興趣的選民如按照上列條件登記，估計選民基數將以倍數增加，四屆動當選的情況應不會再出現。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">個人選民與/團體選民</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因上述工會可能有公司/團體會員與個人會員之分別，故有意成為選民的可選擇如下。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>個人</strong><br />\n(a) 請填寫表格REO-41（&ldquo;功能界別選民及/或選舉委員會界別分組投票人個人登記申請表&rdquo;）；(b)申請登記在這個功能界別及一個選舉委員會界別分組。 如你想更改功能界別選民及/或選舉委員會界別分組投票人個人登記資料/取消登記或不登記於區議會（第二）功能界別申請表&rdquo;請填寫REO-43。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C%29.pdf&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA6NZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=4e14ab73\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C).pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-43(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-43%28C%29.pdf&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA6NZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=753e8cdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-43(C).pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>團體</strong><br />\n(b) 請填寫表格REO-42（&ldquo;功能界別選民及／或選舉委員會界別分組投票人團體登記／更改登記資料申請表&rdquo;）。團體也可委任獲授權代表投票(只適用於團體) ，獲授權代表的資格如下 ：<br />\n(1) 已登記為地方選區選民，或有資格登記為地方選區選民，並已申請作如此登記及<br />\n(2) 與申請登記的團體有密切聯繫，例如獲授權代表是申請團體的成員、會員、合夥人、高級人員、人員或僱員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-42(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-42%28C%29.pdf&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA6NZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=68ab9f0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-42(C).pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>新註冊選民請盡可能在5月2日前登記<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原有「超級區議會」選民，請在4月1日前提交申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></div></span><br />\n<br />\n當你登記為進出口界功能界別選民，將有權在立法會及選舉委員會界別分組換屆選舉或補選中投票，請記緊於如果你要在2020年9月在立法會選舉時，在進出口界功能組別上投票，你必須2020年5月2日前完成登記，否則將不能投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過若你在2020年5月2日後才完成登記，仍可以參加2021年12月的選舉委員會投票，選出選委，該等選委將可2022年行政長官選舉上投票。"},{"pid":"26b598296f19e9e8431418cb0271d85ad13a4766","tid":1852557,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea90d96a4968eafe2e89afeb0bf9b8f353a53c71","tid":1852557,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbc217e3cb0b6066426f8bf97648160f3ae6d4b","tid":1852557,"uid":68182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:47:44.000Z","msg":"有用post 推<br />\n但呢個界別同漁農業一樣難打破<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673a88118d1b76f007c1850536c67f8a699ddd9c","tid":1852557,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T01:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e3061009eb07b792d17c8a4bf4170cc1a2c61b8","tid":1852557,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5ac9c96a9ce0099698d34168a9f80aefb66a0b","tid":1852557,"uid":126054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T06:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"996abbc66a7b7cd7dbce986a4d3f21dc33ae93e9","tid":1852557,"uid":19640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T06:13:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8840ef73ba8812103ab7df9f94027350c097fae","tid":1852557,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592db04039a15135978be6c0c746e61fadc9fcb6","tid":1852557,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:01:06.000Z","msg":"立法會功能組別攻略、組工會TG總公海 <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Cd9xTVNjRXjQUQuoWiSPDw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FCd9xTVNjRXjQUQuoWiSPDw&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA6NZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=7de67cc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Cd9xTVNjRXjQUQuoWiSPDw</a> <br />\n<br />\n18區召集飲食界channel🍿 <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/cateringvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcateringvote&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA6NZBGycwMyv8OGD44uL